meanings.definition: Decorated or dyed using a wax-resist dyeing technique known as batik.
meanings.sent1: The batiked fabric had intricate patterns created through the batik process.
meanings.sent2: She wore a beautiful batiked dress to the cultural festival.
meanings.sent3: The batiked tablecloth looked like a work of art at the picnic.
meanings.sent4: The batiked tapestry told a story through its colorful designs.
meanings.sent5: The batiked pillow added a touch of elegance to the room.
